         <div type="commentary" subtype="frontmatter" xml:space="preserve">
        <p>This papyrus has been digitally edited by Ilaria Andrea Serra during a workshop organized at the University of Florence by Valeria Piano (Univ. of Florence) with James Cowey (instructor; Univ. of Heidelberg) and Claudio Vergara (assistant; Univ. of Naples Federico II) within the project PRIN2022-INTEGRATION. INTEllectual miGRATION: circulation of philosophical books and ideas around the ancient Mediterranean through the evidence of Graeco-Romani papyri (CUP: B53D23023140006; P.I. Valeria Piano)</p>
      </div>
         <div xml:lang="grc" type="edition" xml:space="preserve">
<ab>
<lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/>.<gap reason="lost" atLeast="1" atMost="2" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="4" unit="character"/>αμ<gap reason="illegible" quantity="5" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>

<lb n="2" break="no" xml:id="lb2"/><app type="alternative"><lem>σαι δ’ εἶναι</lem><rdg>σαι δειναί</rdg></app>, τῆς περὶ <expan>ἕκαστο<ex>ν</ex></expan>

<lb n="3"/>λεγομένης τῶν σωμάτων

<lb n="4"/>δυάδος ἀδιάγνωστον αἰσθή

<lb n="5" break="no"/>σει τὴν δ<supplied reason="lost">ι</supplied>αφορὰν ἐχούσης.

<lb n="6"/>εἰ γὰρ σῶμα μὲν <hi rend="diaeresis">ἰ</hi>δίως ποι-

<lb n="7"/>ὸν οἷον Πλάτων, σῶμα <app type="editorial"><lem resp="Long-Sedley"><unclear>θ</unclear>’ ἡ</lem><rdg resp="ed.pr."><gap reason="illegible" quantity="3" unit="character"/></rdg></app>

<lb n="8"/>οὐσία τοῦ Πλάτωνος, διαφορὰ

<lb n="9"/>δὲ φαινομένη τούτων οὔκ ἐ

<lb n="10" break="no"/>στιν οὔτε σχήματος οὔτε<g rend="dot" type="filler"/>

<lb n="11"/>χρώματος οὔτε μεγέθους οὔ<supplied reason="omitted">τε</supplied>

<lb n="12"/>μορφῆς, ἀλλὰ καὶ βάρος <hi rend="diaeresis">ἴ</hi>σον

<lb n="13" xml:id="lb13"/>καὶ <app type="editorial"><lem>τ<unclear>ό</unclear>πος</lem><rdg resp="Irwin">τ<supplied reason="lost">ό</supplied>πος</rdg><rdg resp="ed.pr.">τ<supplied reason="lost">ύ</supplied>πος</rdg></app> ὁ αὐτὸς ἀμφοτέ

<lb n="14" break="no"/>ρων, τίνι διαιροῦντες ὅρῳ

<lb n="15"/>κ<supplied reason="lost">αὶ</supplied> χαρακτῆρι νῦν μὲν<g rend="dot" type="filler"/>

<lb n="16"/>φήσ<supplied reason="lost">ο</supplied>μεν αὐτοῦ Πλάτωνος

<lb n="17"/>νῦν δὲ τῆς οὐσίας ἀντιλαμ

<lb n="18" break="no"/>βάνεσθαι τῆς Πλάτωνος;<g type="middot"/>

<lb n="19"/>εἰ μὲν γάρ ἐστ<unclear>ί</unclear>ν τις διαφο

<lb n="20" break="no"/>ρά, λεγέσθω μ<unclear>ε</unclear>τὰ ἀποδεί

<lb n="21" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost">ξεω</supplied>ς· εἰ δὲ μηδὲ λέγειν
</ab></div>
